stateDiagram-v2
    state "No incident" as NoIncident
    state "Open<br/>resourceHold = true" as Open
    state "Acknowledged<br/>resourceHold = true" as Acknowledged
    state "Resolved<br/>resourceHold = false" as Resolved

    [*] --> NoIncident
    NoIncident --> Open: outcome mismatch or inconclusive
    Open --> Acknowledged: reviewer acknowledges and investigates
    Acknowledged --> Resolved: authorized resolution recorded
    Open --> Resolved: authorized direct resolution
    Resolved --> [*]

    Open --> Open: authenticated re-verification remains mismatch / inconclusive
    Acknowledged --> Acknowledged: investigation evidence added (required)

    note right of Open
        Current API: list, get, acknowledge or resolve.
        Resolution uses caller-supplied identity in the preview.
    end note

    note right of Resolved
        No automatic rollback.
        Compensation is a new governed Action Claim.
    end note
